snippet.title: MapleStory | GO WEST! Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready to GO WEST! with the most exciting 🍁MapleStory update of the year?! 
MapleStory GO WEST! launches June 12th.

#MapleStory #Inkwell #AngelicBuster #GOWEST #HyperBurning #Maplers

👉 New localized direction with the Maple Boys, Inkwell and Dr. Lim 🎶
🔥Hyper Burning & Tera Blink 👉 Level up to Lv. 260 with massive EXP bonuses
🎙Angelic Buster Remaster 👉 queen of music, Angelic Buster, has blessed us with her return

Play MapleStory Now ⏭ https://gsght.com/c/hyjyji
